                Task cards
                <svg class="chevron w-3 h-3 text-gray-400 shrink-0 hidden" style="transition: transform 0.5s ease;" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M2 4l4 4 4-4"/></svg>
              </summary>
              <div class="accordion-content overflow-hidden">
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mt-2">Tasks are presented as simple cards with a checkbox and short description, making the setup feel approachable, lightweight, and easy to complete.</p>
